                    </a>
                    <a href="https://discord.gg/m5Hknymurb" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
